task.summary: New Navigation Drawer Layout with profile photo
Testing and beginning to incorporate Retrofix for network APIs, Butterknife to remove findViewByID and Picasso for profile image. User stays logged in.
Adding user profile page. User can now add user details. Alert dialog pops up to ask the user if they really want to exit the app when user hits backspace to exit the app.
Divider added to recycler view, two buttons (Contact and bookmark) has been added. Background for recycler view now in black and white.
UI for changing user image. Favorite feature to bookmark other user's posts.

User can save favorite posts and have it saved and displayed back on the recyclerview. Changing profile picture is improved. Picasso now only reloads the profile image when necessary. User can now delete their posts.
User profile displays the city through location service. Beginning to incorporate tabs into find buddy option.
Find buddy fragment can now find nearby users.

Sign up process now pass intent extra between activities so sign up process will take place only when the user provides all needed information. Added sign up part 3 to include option to provide profile picture at sign up. Service is now used to broadcast to the Main User page to listen for and update user location only if the current location is 30 meters from last known location.
